<section class="inner">
<div class="text flt-left">
<h1><span style="color: #3791cf;">Hi, I’m Richard Pearson</span> and I’ve been helping clients “Building Brands” for over 10 years, after my earlier career in companies like Cadbury’s, U.B. &amp; Princes.</h1>
<p>My approach is very flexible, commercial &amp; “hands-on” covering all key aspects of “Building Brands”:</p>
<ul style="list-style: disc; list-style-position: inside;">
<li>New brand development</li>
<li>Re-vitalising existing brands</li>
<li>Uncovering new distribution channels</li>
<li>Selling it in to the trade.</li>
<li>Getting the right people in place</li>
</ul>
<p>Food &amp; Drink is my speciality, having worked in most key categories including Frozen, Chilled, Ambient – Long-life, Snacks, Confectionery, Soft Drinks etc.</p>
<p>But don’t just take my word for it, have a look at some of the ways we’ve helped our clients overcome key issues to successfully build their brands…</p>
</div>
<div class="image flt-right">
<img src="http://www.richardpearsonmarketing.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/richard-pearson1.jpg" alt="" /></div>
