<article class="block-three" id="about">
<section class="inner">
<h2 class="page-name">What We Do</h2>
<div class="text flt-left">
<p>Understanding the critical dynamics of a specific category using market data analysis, store-checks, competitor studies, consumer research etc.</p>

<p>Managing major brand projects such as re-launches,  new product launches, on-line initiatives to ensure all delivered to time &amp; cost constraints.</p>

<p>Uncovering new distribution channels for brands, through trade sector analysis, bespoke approaches, investigating new routes to market, 3rd Party joint ventures, etc.</p>

<p>Taking on the actual Sales representation for certain clients, particularly to secure support from the Major Multiple Supermarkets & Convenience trade sectors.</p>

<p>Optimising key commercial personnel to deliver brand growth for clients by a range of services from finding the best people to the coaching & development of existing personnel on a “one on one” basis.</p>
<div id="test1"><p style="text-align:center;font-size: 1px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 91px;">test</p></div>
</div>

